short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects Graphite pull request URLs to GitHub

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tired of the Graphite CLI opening pull requests in the Graphite web reviewer?  This extension has your back and will automatically redirects navigations from Graphite to GitHub when viewing pull request pages.  You can still navigate to the Graphite dashboard directly to view notifications, settings, and more.
